    <text x="20" y="32" fill="#fafafa" font-size="17" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">The Buyback Logic Flips — Before vs. Aavenomics 3.0</text>
    <text x="20" y="56" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">What matters is which side is the "default"</text>
